ASIA PACKAGED
TBI Tours and United Airlines have packages to Asia that start at $ 899 for six nights in Beijing , including air fare from Los Angeles .
A four-night Best Buy Hong Kong tour starts at $ 969 ; a five-night Best Buy Beijing and Tokyo starts at $ 1 , 099 , and a six-night Beijing and Hong Kong combination at $ 1 , 489 .
From the East Coast , additional air fare ranges from $ 65 to $ 100 a person round trip , depending on the tour .
The lowest prices are for departures late this year , with peak summer travel running up to $ 230 more .
Optional excursions and extra nights ' lodging are available .
More information and reservations : ( 800 ) 223 - 0266 .
NEW YORK SUMMER
The Hotel Inter-Continental at Park Avenue and 48th Street in Manhattan has a rate of $ 199 for a room ( single or double occupancy ) and $ 299 for a suite on weekends this summer , with a bonus : Hotel amenities and services will be discounted 50 percent , including food and beverage , health club services and phone calls .
These rates are offered from June 25 to Aug. 16 ; they are available on Friday , Saturday and Sunday nights , and also on Thursday if guests are staying through Saturday night .
Information and reservations : ( 212 ) 755 - 5900 or ( 800 ) 327 - 0200 .
PARIS ON SALE
Air France Holidays has introduced a Paris on Sale package starting at $ 899 a person , double occupancy , from New York , including round-trip air fare , five nights ' accommodation at the Meridien Montparnasse or Etoile , service , VAT and Continental breakfast daily .
The same price applies to departures from Newark or from Boston , where Air France starts service June 19 .
The package must be purchased by June 15 for travel between July 13 and Aug. 31 .
Other cities are available at higher prices .
Customs and departure taxes are extra .
Reservations : ( 800 ) 237 - 2623 .
